culation (pass/fail counts)\n  - Recent run history (last 10 runs)\n  - Active run count\n  - Project labels and directories\n\n**10. Configuration (`internal/config/config.go`)**\n- Per-project config: `active`, `daemon` (listen, HTTP, image, db, runtime, agent_path, llm_command), `evolution`, `orchestration` settings\n- Orchestration settings: `concurrency`, `stagger_seconds`, `list_tasks_command`, `dedup_seconds`, `stop_on_error`\n\n**11. Version System**\n- Version stored in `/workspace/internal/version/VERSION` (currently \"1.4.2\")\n- `GetVersion()` RPC returns version string\n- CLI `cloche -v` shows CLI, daemon, and agent versions\n\n### Key Files for Implementation\n\n- **Proto definition**: `/workspace/api/proto/cloche/v1/cloche.proto` (lines 1-169)\n- **gRPC server**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/grpc/server.go` (1354 lines)\n- **CLI status command**: `/workspace/cmd/cloche/main.go` (cmdStatus at line 223)\n- **CLI project command**: `/workspace/cmd/cloche/project.go` (cmdProject at line 14)\n- **CLI list command**: `/workspace/cmd/cloche/main.go` (cmdList at line 262)\n- **Domain types**: `/workspace/internal/domain/run.go` (195 lines)\n- **Store interface**: `/workspace/internal/ports/store.go` (60 lines)\n- **Config**: `/workspace/internal/config/config.go` (119 lines)\n- **Web handler**: `/workspace/internal/adapters/web/handler.go` (1800+ lines)\n\n### Available Data for Daemon Status Overview\n\nFrom gRPC server and store, you can retrieve:\n1. **All projects** via `store.ListProjects()`\n2. **Per-project runs** via `store.ListRunsByProject(projectDir, since)`\n3. **Orchestration loops status** via `server.loops` map (active/halted/stopped)\n4. **Per-project config** via `config.Load(projectDir)`\n5. **Container runtime state** via `container.Inspect()` for running containers\n6. **Run aggregates**:\n   - Total runs, active runs, succeeded/failed/cancelled counts\n   - Health status (pass rate)\n   - Recent activity timeline\n7. **Agent/daemon/container image version** via existing GetVersion() RPC\n\n### Implementation Strategy Points\n\n1. **Proto addition needed**: New RPC like `GetDaemonStatus()` or `GetDaemonOverview()` returning daemon-wide metrics\n2. **gRPC server implementation**: Aggregates data across all projects from store and loop state\n3. **CLI command**: New command like `cloche daemon status` or `cloche status --all` that calls the new RPC\n4. **Help text pattern**: See `/workspace/cmd/cloche/help.go` for all help text definitions (lines 8-425)\n5. **Output format patterns**: \n   - Human-readable: See `cmdProject()` format\n   - Compact table: See `cmdList()` format\n   - Structured JSON: See web API handlers\n6. **Version bump consideration**: Per CLAUDE.md, assess if feature requires minor/major version bump and tag during finalize workflow\n\nAll absolute file paths provided above for reference during implementation."}],"totalDurationMs":58471,"totalTokens":73064,"totalToolUseCount":34,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":390,"cache_read_input_tokens":70710,"output_tokens":1964,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":390},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
